257
00:29:03.173 --> 00:29:05.641
Nu stii nimic despre bestie.

258
00:29:09.613 --> 00:29:12.138
Eu sunt Raphaella.

259
00:29:12.182 --> 00:29:17.916
Ea care va naste
la visele tanarului pastor.

260
00:29:27.964 --> 00:29:29.329
Ce?

261
00:29:36.239 --> 00:29:38.230
Ce vrei de la mine?

262
00:29:39.576 --> 00:29:40.736
Liniste!

263
00:29:40.777 --> 00:29:42.244
Ajuta-ma.

264
00:29:43.613 --> 00:29:47.174
Elibereaza-ma de fiara
si toate placerile mele vor fi ale tale.

265
00:29:49.352 --> 00:29:51.286
- El aude.
- Huh?

266
00:29:51.321 --> 00:29:56.554
Era o fata
de la ultimul sacrificiu.

267
00:29:56.593 --> 00:29:59.027
Ffion. Spune-mi.

268
00:29:59.062 --> 00:30:01.394
Salveaza-ma si te voi ajuta.

269
00:30:01.431 --> 00:30:02.420
Unde este ea?

270
00:30:02.466 --> 00:30:05.458
Fiara se satura de Raphaella!

271
00:30:07.737 --> 00:30:10.535
Cum indraznesti sa intri in camerele mele?

272
00:30:10.574 --> 00:30:14.874
Te-ai face placut
cu aceasta murdarie.

273
00:30:14.911 --> 00:30:17.243
- Te rog. frate ...
- Ce?!

274
00:30:18.648 --> 00:30:21.378
Nu ma intreba vreodata.

275
00:30:21.418 --> 00:30:23.045
- Ia-l!
- Nu!

276
00:30:43.373 --> 00:30:46.774
Nu te indepartezi niciodata de mine!

277
00:30:46.810 --> 00:30:50.473
Daca aceasta este placerea ta.
atunci asa sa fie.

278
00:30:50.514 --> 00:30:56.350
Te voi corupe
fiecare soldat si sclav din palat!

279
00:30:56.386 --> 00:30:59.253
Te voi arunca la leprosi ...

280
00:30:59.289 --> 00:31:02.281
si priveste-i
tarai-te in interiorul tau!

281
00:31:02.325 --> 00:31:05.317
Atunci cand ma rogi ...

282
00:31:05.362 --> 00:31:08.024
atunci va veni taurul.

283
00:31:10.400 --> 00:31:13.927
Dar mai intai tu. tanar pastor.

284
00:31:24.080 --> 00:31:26.275
Frica.

285
00:31:27.284 --> 00:31:31.516
Miros de teama asupra tanarului cioban.

286
00:31:33.089 --> 00:31:38.857
Cunoasteti frica doar ca un miel
smuls de la mama sa.

287
00:31:38.895 --> 00:31:41.989
O sa-ti arat adevarata teama.

288
00:31:42.032 --> 00:31:45.433
Frica care iti va sfasia inima
din sufletul tau.

289
00:31:45.468 --> 00:31:48.835
Teama care va face
spiritul tau se agita!

290
00:31:48.872 --> 00:31:51.568
Te fac sa-ti doresti ca ochii tai
s-au nascut orbi ...

291
00:31:51.608 --> 00:31:53.235
inchis sigilat!

292
00:31:53.276 --> 00:31:55.335
Pentru el te duci.

293
00:32:01.451 --> 00:32:03.612
Sa fie intunericul lui.

294
00:32:03.653 --> 00:32:04.881
Unde esti?

295
00:32:46.129 --> 00:32:47.221
Didi!

296
00:32:49.733 --> 00:32:52.133
Ajutor! Morna! Theo!

297
00:33:10.086 --> 00:33:11.280
Scoate-ma de aici!

298
00:33:28.238 --> 00:33:30.433
Theo!

299
00:34:25.261 --> 00:34:27.957
Nu cereti jertfa.

300
00:34:28.498 --> 00:34:32.400
Va rog sa nu ma urati. stapane.

301
00:34:32.435 --> 00:34:34.767
Te urasc?

302
